[55.174766, "o", "Three Frame-phase artifacts created:\r\n\r\n- `docs/helix/00-discover/product-vision.md` вЂ” mission, target users, success criteria, non-goals (~30 lines)\r\n- `docs/helix/01-frame/prd.md` вЂ” CLI interface spec, P0/P1/P2 feature tables, formulas (~50 lines)\r\n- `docs/helix/01-frame/features/FEAT-001-temperature-conversion.md` вЂ” three user stories with acceptance criteria covering the exact test cases you specified (~40 lines)\r\n\r\n"]
