[293.88607, "o", "\r\nWhat you just saw:\r\n  1. Install   вЂ” HELIX skills and CLI set up\r\n  2. Setup     вЂ” git repo, tracker, AGENTS.md\r\n  3. Frame     вЂ” vision, PRD, feature spec created by agent\r\n  4. Design    вЂ” technical design and tracker issues\r\n"]
[293.886121, "o", "  5. Build     вЂ” TDD: failing tests (Red) then implementation (Green)\r\n  6. Verify    вЂ” tests pass, acceptance criteria checked\r\n  7. Review    вЂ” agent reviews its own work\r\n\r\nThe HELIX lifecycle: Frame в†’ Design в†’ Test в†’ Build в†’ Review\r\nThe tracker drives. Artifacts govern. Agents execute.\r\n"]
[293.886162, "o", "\r\n"]
